A command-line tool for generating Julia set fractals.

Usage
=====

```bash
python run.py <density-pixel> <detail-density> <cr> <ci> [options]
```

Example
-----

```bash
python run.py 500 300 -0.4 0.6 -c "inferno" -s "output.jpg"
```

Use `--help` for detailed information about all available options.
